OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted0;

ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted0;

ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

(@p70, @p71, @p72, @p73, @p74, @p75, @p76, @p77, @p78, @p79, 7),
(@p80, @p81, @p82, @p83, @p84, @p85, @p86, @p87, @p88, @p89, 8),
(@p90, @p91, @p92, @p93, @p94, @p95, @p96, @p97, @p98, @p99, 9)) AS i ([Author], [CreatedOn], [Description], [FeedUrl], [Link], [ModifiedOn], [PubDate], [RssFeedId], [Title], [UrlToImage], _Position) ON 1=0
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([Author], [CreatedOn], [Description], [FeedUrl], [Link], [ModifiedOn], [PubDate], [RssFeedId], [Title], [UrlToImage])
VALUES (i.[Author], i.[CreatedOn], i.[Description], i.[FeedUrl], i.[Link], i.[ModifiedOn], i.[PubDate], i.[RssFeedId], i.[Title], i.[UrlToImage])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted0;

SELECT [i].[Id] FROM @inserted0 i
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

ORDER BY [i].[_Position];

VALUES (@p0, @p1, @p2, @p3, @p4, @p5, @p6, @p7, @p8, @p9, 0),
(@p10, @p11, @p12, @p13, @p14, @p15, @p16, @p17, @p18, @p19, 1),

WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
INSERT ([Author], [CreatedOn], [Description], [FeedUrl], [Link], [ModifiedOn], [PubDate], [RssFeedId], [Title], [UrlToImage])
VALUES (i.[Author], i.[CreatedOn], i.[Description], i.[FeedUrl], i.[Link], i.[ModifiedOn], i.[PubDate], i.[RssFeedId], i.[Title], i.[UrlToImage])
OUTPUT INSERTED.[Id], i._Position
INTO @inserted0;

SELECT [i].[Id] FROM @inserted0 i
ORDER BY [i].[_Position];
